              Quick usage instructuins for FlexCat v1.4
             ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
  Usage examples:
      "heqa_app.cd"     is the Catalog Description file for the program
      "heqa_app.ct"     is the Catalog Translation file for the program

  Create an empty .ct file:
      FlexCat heqa_app.cd NEWCTFILE heqa_app.ct

  Create the .catalog file:
      flexcat heqa_app.cd heqa_app.ct CATALOG Headquarters.catalog

  Place the .catalog file in Locale:Catalogs/<language>/ directory and change
  the locale prefs to the language you just created. The Catalogs directory
  can also be placed in the programs home directory.

